org.webcurator.domain.model.core
Class ProfileOverrides

java.lang.Object
  org.webcurator.domain.model.core.ProfileOverrides

public class ProfileOverrides
extends java.lang.Object

Represents a set of overrides that can be applied to a Heritrix profile. Each overridable setting has a value and an on/off setting, allowing the overrides to override something in the default profile with an empty setting.

apply

public void apply(HeritrixProfile profile)
Apply the profile overrides to a Heritrix profile. For each element in the profile that is overriden (the flag set to true), this method deletes the value from the base profile and replaces it with the value from the overrides.

Parameters:
profile - The Heritrix Profile to override.
